org.promasi.core
Interface ISdObject

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractSdObject, FlowSdObject, OutputSdObject, StockSdObject, TimeSdObject, VariableSdObject
public interface ISdObject

Basic interface that represents an object in a system dynamic model(stock,flow etc). An ISdObject has the following characteristics:

  1. An ISdObject is represented in the system by a key.
  2. An ISdObject has a type(SdObjectType) which represents the role of the object in the system.
  3. An ISdObject has a value used by the system.
  4. An ISdObject might depend on other objects in order to calculate its value.

Author:
eddiefullmetal
